      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... she has her own life, her own kids. i'm just an extra weight she's carrying around. i've spent my whole life taking care of others, and now that it's reversed, it feels so wrong. like i'm taking up space that doesn't belong to me anymore. i just want to make things easier for her.",
